source.name: SSMMA Available Buildings
source.description: This dataset includes Available Buildings for Sale or Lease in the Chicago Southland region. This list is a aggregation of data from Wm C Groebe & Co, Lee & Associates, Newmark, Knight, and Frank, Simborg, and Rofo data.
